Waxman Industries Inc. said it has called for optional redemption Nov. 1 for half of its 6.25% convertible subordinated debentures due March 15, 2007. 

The maker of plumbing, electrical and hardware products said the redemption price would be 105% of the principal amount of $12.5 million, constituting one-half of the principal amount of the debentures outstanding. 

